code: @Test public void testSelectOneWithOutputHeader() throws Exception {     MockEndpoint mock = getMockEndpoint("mock:result").     mock.expectedMessageCount(1).     mock.message(0).header(TEST_CASE_HEADER_NAME).isInstanceOf(Account.class).     mock.message(0).body().isEqualTo(TEST_ACCOUNT_ID).     mock.message(0).header(MyBatisConstants.MYBATIS_RESULT).isNull().     template.sendBody("direct:start", TEST_ACCOUNT_ID).     assertMockEndpointsSatisfied().
